articles.title: Outcry as Australian police Taser 95-year-old care home resident - BBC
articles.description: Care home resident Clare Nowland is not expected to survive the incident, a family friend says.
articles.content:
An elderly Australian woman with dementia is in hospital with life-threatening injuries after being Tasered by police at a care home.
